creator: Selfloops
descriptionHtml:
The Selfloops Group Premium is an application for real-time telemetry of heart rate monitors and bike power sensors and is ideal for group workouts and trainings.

Concept2 rowers and SkiErg are supported too. And the Stryd sensor for running power.

The scope of the app is to train more effectively when real-time intensity feedback is given. With this app coaches can monitor their classes and train people according to their heart rate and bike power zones.



WHAT YOU NEED
An Android device with USB Host support, an ANT stick and a USB OTG cable.

Please install the ANT Radio Service, the USB ANT Service and the ANT+ Plugins Service.

You can use any ANT+ certified heart rate monitor, like Garmin and Wahoo Fitness Tickr.
You can use it with any ANT+ bike power meter such as the Garmin Vector, SRM, PowerTap, Stages, Wahoo, 4iiii Precision, Fitness Kickr and many others.

The application supports Concept2 rowers and SkiErg too.

Visit our website for more info: http://www.selfloops.com/products/groupfitness.html
